videos.headline: Troy scores on long TD pass
videos.description: Brandon Silvers finds John Johnson wide open in the middle of the field who bursts down the field and scores from 49 yards out.

videos.headline: Silvers throws 2nd TD pass
videos.description: A quick slant route by Deondre Douglas leads to a touchdown throw from Brandon Silvers.

videos.headline: 4th down conversion turns into TD for Troy
videos.description: On 4th and 1, Troy runs a reverse to Deondre Douglas who takes it all the way up the sideline for the 35-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Troy with costly turnover on punt
videos.description: Sidney Davis is back to receive the rugby-style kick and is unable to handle it. Jonathan Ifedi comes in from behind and recovers.

videos.headline: Troy bounces back from loss with big win over Georgia State
videos.description: The Trojans' offense was clicking and the defense was difficult to penetrate in their victory over the Panthers.
